column5: Happy birthday Roy, hope you have the best day hon.  Joey
Happy B Day Roy, my wife and you share a birthday hers today as well. Moon landing day, July 20th 1969. I think 69'.
All the best to you Roy
Happy Birthday, I hope you have a good one
Hope got out to fish on your birthday me brudder.  Have a super day.
Happy birthday Roy, hope you have a good one!
Happy birthday Roy aka papa smurf lol
Happy birthday Roy!!,hope you have a awesome day!
Cheers to you on you're birthday my brother.
he hasn't answered yet so I am guessing he's out fishing
Happy Birthday me friend See you all soon.   Art
Another day older! How the heck did that happen?  All the very best to you my friend!
Hey Roy.   Happy birthday to you from Norma and me in cabin 3 on Little Vermilion Lake.  I'll lift one to you before hitting the sack.   Chasing pike and walleyes has worn us down.
Thank you so much everyone for the birthday wishes. I had a wonderful weekend!

Happy belated birday Roy...don't know how I missed it...I got it marked on my calendar...I guess I need to look at it once in a while...  Oh well, like our pal Jack used to say..."It's me age, don't you know"...
